# Server backend

Entry: `server.ts` (bundle → `dist/server.cjs`)

## Модули (server/)

dataStore.ts, apiAuth.ts, sessionEngine.ts, userCredentials.ts, passwordHash.ts, licenseCore.ts, updateEngine.ts, notificationDispatch.ts, workspaceSeed.json

## API (основное)

| Method | Path | Назначение |
|--------|------|------------|
| GET | `/api/health` | Health + version |
| GET/POST | `/api/auth/*` | Setup, login, sessions |
| GET/POST | `/api/data` | Workspace CRUD + revision |
| GET/POST | `/api/backup/*` | Backup (Admin) |
| GET/POST | `/api/db-config*` | SQL config (Admin) |
| GET/POST | `/api/update/*` | GitHub auto-update |

## Env

`PORT`, `DB_ENCRYPTION_KEY`, `STACK_DATA_DIR`, `SKIP_OBFUSCATION=true` (Docker build)

При изменении API — синхронно: `src/utils/apiClient.ts`, `sessionAuth.ts`, `workspaceSync.ts`.
